The paper discusses the use of evolutionary strategies and genetic algorithms for target motion analysis, which falls under the category of system and control (cs.SY). The use of these algorithms also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE) for prediction and optimization. The paper also involves statistical analysis and optimization, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and software engineering (cs.SE).
